=09=09=09=09Time for friends
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09At the start of the impeachment trial of President Joseph Estra=
da of the=20
Philippines, a count of his supporters in the Senate suggested that they=20
could be sufficient to prevent his conviction on charges of corruption.=20
Police were on =01&red alert=018 for possible clashes between foes and frie=
nds of=20
the president. An opinion poll gave Mr Estrada a popularity rating of 41%, =
up=20
