=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09Taiwan called on America to lift its ban on visits by Taiwanese=
 officials.=20
President Chen Shui-bian said he feared that Taiwan=01,s interests were bei=
ng=20
sacrificed while America was =01&engaging=018 China.
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09Australia is to increase its spending on defence by almost $13 =
billion during=20
the next decade. The government said Australia would focus on regional=20
threats and contribute more to peacekeeping forces. A defence report=20
complained that Australia could expect little help from =01&useless=018 New=
 Zealand.
